summary: Adds Enelya as a racemenu preset.
descriptionHtml:
This is a racemenu preset for my character; Enelya. [s](Additional images will be uploaded shortly, this is posting as a quick share on request)[/s]

Requires:

[list]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/18717/?]Temptress Race[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?tab=1&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmoddescription%2F%3Fid%3D10168%26preview%3D&pUp=1]Apachii Sky Hair[/url] (main & female)
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]Eyes of Beauty[/url]
[/list]
NOT Required, but used and recommended:[list]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?tab=1&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmoddescription%2F%3Fid%3D35267%26preview%3D&pUp=1]SG Textures (UNP)[/url] 

[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?]Dimonized UNP body[/url] (possibly being overwritten by Temptress body, not sure!)

[/list]
Installation:

[list=1]
[*]Extract the included .jslot file to: Data\SKSE\plugins\chargen\presets

[*]In Racemenu load the preset 'Enelya' from the sculpt tab
[/list]
author: LegacyCloud
